<p><h3>What is teck brick?</h3> Teck brick is a software where you can build Bricks digitally. This software has been coded by the greatest
for top-notch quality and a fun experience. There are two types of tech brick: The first is normal tech brick which is free and has a lot of bricks for your pleasure. There is also Teck brick pro that costs $16 with customisable stickers and extra bricks to make your buildings look even better. This comes on a unique USB that has extra memory space for other things. Imagine how many real building bricks $16 would buy you. Not a lot but with Teck brick you would have access to every brick ever manufactured you could make things that you could never make physically. You can earn or buy points to buy brick sets and brick figures in the app.How do you earn points?, you can enter a daily competition of your builds  to earn points 
<br>
<br>
<h3>How do we make money?</h3> We will make money as we previously said you can buy points, we will also have ads on the side of a page so companies will pay to put them on there. You can also buy teck brick pro.
For $16 dollars we will custom-print a brick figure. For $10 you can enter a tech brick masters competition and try and win 10000 points.
<br>


</p>
